## Memory

Memoria gestionada automaticamente:
- **Capa 1:** `.claude/rules/` (auto-cargado siempre: decisions.md, project-context.md)
- **Capa 2:** Hooks (SessionStart/PreCompact/Stop inyectan/guardan contexto via Engram)
- **Capa 3:** Engram MCP bajo demanda (mem_search, mem_save, mem_context)
- **Herramientas sin hooks:** Consultar Feature Specs en `docs/specs/` como memoria de proyecto.

## Global Guards

- **Zero Trust:** Validate all inputs
- **Clean Arch:** Domain > Application > Infrastructure
- **Logs:** Structured with correlationId
- **TDD:** No production code without failing test first
